  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows three rotating hoops that are labeled “Hoop 1,” “Hoop 2,” and “Hoop 3.”\" src=\"/images/b6f228028710cc39a66560a1ce2e23d7.svg\"></div>\n<p class=\"passage_para\">Three hoops are each rotating about their respective centers, which are fixed in place, as shown in the figure. The mass, radius, and angular speed of each hoop are as follows.</p>\n<ul class=\"unordered_list style:1\">\n<li class=\"list_paragraph\">Hoop <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> has mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m sub 0\"><math alttext=\"m sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span>, radius <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"r sub 0\"><math alttext=\"r sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span>, and angular speed <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"omega sub 0\"><math alttext=\"omega sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span>.</li>\n<li class=\"list_paragraph\">Hoop <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> has mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m sub 0\"><math alttext=\"m sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span>, radius <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction r sub 0 over 2\"><math alttext=\"the fraction r sub 0 over 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></span></span>, and angular speed <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4 omega sub 0\"><math alttext=\"4 omega sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span>.</li>\n<li class=\"list_paragraph\">Hoop <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3\"><math alttext=\"3\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>3</mn></math></span></span> has mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 m sub 0\"><math alttext=\"2 m sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span>, radius <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 r sub 0\"><math alttext=\"2 r sub 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><msub><mi>r</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math></span></span>, and angular speed <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction omega sub 0 over 2\"><math alttext=\"the fraction omega sub 0 over 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><msub><mi>ω</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></span></span>.</li>\n</ul>\n</div></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">How do the total kinetic energies <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub 1\"><math alttext=\"K sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span>, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub 2\"><math alttext=\"K sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span>, and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"K sub 3\"><math alttext=\"K sub 3\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>K</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></math></span></span> of the three hoops compare to one another?</p>\n",
